On Thu, 21 Jul 2022 16:22:08 +0100,
Frank Li <frank.li@nxp.com> wrote:
> 
> > > +     pos = find_first_zero_bit(&msi_data->used, IMX_MU_CHANS);
> > > +     if (pos < IMX_MU_CHANS)
> > > +             __set_bit(pos, &msi_data->used);
> > > +     else
> > > +             err = -ENOSPC;
> > > +     spin_unlock(&msi_data->lock);
> > > +
